description: This Chainlink VRF common Sakura purrs with a rating of 46, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 92, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, Box for East, 3 for South, and 8 for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10462-44380-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [92 Votes, Common]
